description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 55, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 55, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 2 for East, Leverage for South, and 5 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [55 Votes, Common]
